answers.textfield_31440655: Two Systems: Apricot (client management system) and EMS Data Warehouse
answers.textarea_31444284: The Apricot client management system is used to identify CHP clients, and to determine the duration of their enrollment in the program. This is currently done on an as-needed basis.
